<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Installing the Composer</div><div><br /></div><div># Update the Ports Tree</div><div>=&gt; sudo portsnap fetch update</div><div># Install the composer from the ports</div><div>=&gt; cd /usr/ports/devel/php-composer</div><div>=&gt; sudo make install clean</div><div># This will install the Composer</div><div># Version: php71-composer-1.6.3</div></en-note>